LJava
Class Variable

java.lang.Object
  LJava.Variable

public class Variable
extends java.lang.Object

Author:
Tzali Maimon The variables in LJ are represented by this class.

This class isn't totally immutable. A variable turns immutable only after first instantiation.

getConstraint

public final Constraint getConstraint()
Returns:
the constraint of the variable. A constraint of a variable serves as OR. meaning that if a vairable has a value of 2 and a constraint of "greater than 4" then 2 is a value, 10 is a value, 50 is a value but not 3.
